data.description: A Large Driveway leads up to the coveted "Patio Home" and this one has a Sun Room along with a Screened Porch and Patio!  Nice yard and room to move around in the back with privacy. Lovely floor plan w Large Family Room - Kitchen has a Breakfast Bar w Quartz Countertops - all appliances included!   The kitchen is open and everything very convenient!   Large Primary BR & Bath along with Walk In Closet.  Second BR is a nice size along with a full bath.   Laundry Room.
